          <p class="text-sky-700 font-black">Mobile-optimized = view anywhere = book anywhere.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-blue-50 border-[3px] border-sky-300 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">5. No Guide Credentials = No Premium Pricing</h3>
