        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-blue-50 border-[3px] border-sky-300 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">6. Difficult Booking = Abandoned Bookings</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>The trap:</strong> "Email us to book your tour."</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Reality:</strong> "Email us to book" in 2025? Travelers want to BOOK NOW, not start email chains. Online booking with deposit: secure spot immediately. Email inquiry: lose 40% to competitors with instant booking. Online booking systems cost $30-50/month. Lose 40% of bookings to save $30/month? Bad math.</p>
